transcript.text: Hello everyone, I hope you're doing well
Today I will show you this beauty pumpkin
It's kinda easy to do
with some regular products and if you like it
keep on watching!
I start by doing my base with Total control foundation by NYX
And work it with my beauty blender
I apply my concealer
mine is from Maybelline and I hate it
To contour my face in an orange shade
I use my flash color palette and mix yellow and red
An I work it with my beauty blender
To set everything I use a white
loose powder with a puff
To intensify the contour I use an orange matte shadow
I do my brows in a regular way
For my light points I use Star Powder 940
from MUFE and I apply it on my cheeks
nose and chin
I start my eyes by applying an orange pencil
from LH Cosmetics and I do my bases with
black aqua magic from MUFE
I blend my crayon
I add an orange base on my lids
I put my shadows now so I start with the black one
it's from Ride or Die palette from Violet Voss
I use Alice from the same palette as my transition shade
because it's too hard to blend the 2 colors together I add
some warm brown (josie) between them
I use Homeoplasmine as glitter glue
and I apply it on my lids
only where I want the glitters to be
I put the glitters directly on top
If you didn't put enough powder just like me
glitters may be fixed on your skin so if the brush doesn't
work, just take some tape and put on your hand to
remove the sticky effect and put it on your skin
to take off the glitters without ruining your base
I do my eyeliner, the whole process
is linked in the description box
With the same brush and liner
I draw the nose in a random shape
I put Cosmic Kitten from Rouge and Rogue
I add some light on my inner corner
I draw the shape of my mouth with a beige pencil
and I fill it with Friday from Colourpop
I precise the shape with the same lipstick
and a flat brush
I will put some glitters under my eyes
so I take again the Homeoplasmine
put it on the desired area, and put
the glitters on top
I do the same on my nose
My wig is from Donalovehair
This video is finished I hope you enjoyed it
share your thoughts in the comment section
don't hesitate to subscribe and turn on notifications
so you will know when I'm uploading new videos
See you tomorrow!
